Subject: Re: [T2] Perplexing Oil Leak(s)

get all 5 plugs tapped and then screw in replacement plugs.  I've had 
one pop out in the rear of the engine and one in the front.  You'll dump 
out your oil *real* quick if they pop out.

Mike

